title: Can I transfer my League acc from Garena to OCE server?
body:
I've been playing league in Philippines since season 3 but I had to move to OCE server so is there a way to transfer my PH server acc to OCE server?

Thanks!

replies.body:
Hey there,

Unfortunately, no.

Transfers to/from garena regions are a lot more complicated than transferring to/from Riot owned regions and were only opened up for a limited time when OCE was launched.
